other non-source files of a program from the program's source files.
dependencies.name: gmake

dependent_to.description:
RepeatMasker is a program that screens DNA sequences for interspersed
repeats and low complexity DNA sequences.
dependent_to.name: repeatmasker

description:
phrap is a program for assembling shotgun DNA sequence data. cross_match
is a general purpose utility for comparing any two DNA sequence sets
using a 'banded' version of swat. swat is a program for searching one or
more DNA or protein query sequences, or a query profile, against a
sequence database
name: phrap-crossmatch-swat
